Bugs
~~~~

No bugs, of course. ;-)
But if you've found one or have an idea how to improve the WTF, feel
free to send a pull request on `github
<https://github.com/ndparker/wtf>`_ or send a mail to
<wtf-bugs@perlig.de>.


